data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nestled in the heart of Davenport, Florida, this exceptional 4-bedroom with TWO Master En-suites, a 3-bathroom residence with the second master bath fully remodeled, presents a unique opportunity as both a cherished primary residence and a lucrative vacation rental. AC is 2 years old, Pool Pump is 1 year old, Brand New Stainless Steel Appliances, and Brand New Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring. Situated within a secure gated community, this home offers a blend of comfort, convenience, and easy access to the enchantment of Disney World, a mere 30-minute drive away.    Key Features:    Flexible Living Space: This thoughtfully designed layout provides versatile living spaces, seamlessly accommodating the needs of both homeowners and guests.    Fully-Equipped Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen is equipped with Brand New Stainless Steel Modern Appliances, ample storage, and a breakfast bar, making it a focal point for gatherings and culinary delights.    Private Master Retreat: The master suite offers a peaceful sanctuary, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bath featuring a luxurious soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities.    Guest Comfort: Three additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer flexibility for family, friends, or even home office use.    Outdoor Oasis: Step onto the screened lanai with an oversized heated pool and jacuzzi to enjoy the Florida sunshine or host gatherings in the expansive backyard, surrounded by lush landscaping and mature trees.    Endless Potential for Rental Income: This property boasts the potential to serve as a lucrative vacation rental, capitalizing on its prime location near Disney and the allure of a gated community.    Community Perks: Take advantage of the added security and amenities that come with residing in a gated community, providing peace of mind and a range of shared spaces for leisure.    Embrace the opportunity to own a residence that effortlessly balances the comforts of home with the allure of a sought-after vacation destination. Don't miss out on this rare gem!
